sequenceDiagram
  participant Client as 客户端
  participant Hono
  participant BetterAuth as Better Auth
  participant DB as 数据库

  Client->>Hono: 提交登录请求 POST /api/auth/sign-in/email
  Hono->>BetterAuth: 调用 auth.handler(request)
  BetterAuth->>DB: 校验用户并创建 session
  DB-->>BetterAuth: 返回 session
  BetterAuth-->>Hono: 写入 cookie 并返回原生响应
  Hono-->>Client: 返回 auth 原生响应

  Client->>Hono: 读取当前用户 GET /api/v1/me
  Hono->>BetterAuth: 调用 auth.api.getSession(headers)
  BetterAuth->>DB: 读取 session
  DB-->>BetterAuth: 返回 user/session
  BetterAuth-->>Hono: 返回 user/session
  Hono-->>Client: 返回统一 envelope 业务响应
